      "text": "GREAT WORK! #YourFDLE and our federal and local partners teamed up to arrest these illegal aliens from Jamaica who were involved in the distribution of fentanyl in the Florida Panhandle. \n\nPartnerships like these help to make our immigration operations more effective and efficient, keeping these lethal drugs off our streets and illegal aliens out of Florida’s communities.\n\nThank you @EROMiami, @CBPAMO, @DEAMIAMIDiv, @FBIJacksonville, @ATF_Tampa, @BayCountySO and @PanamaCityPd for your continued partnership on these operations!",
